---
const contactEmail = "contact@pyqhintl.com";

---

<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>关于我们 — Pyq Tea</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --green: #4a7c3a;
      --green-dark: #2d5a27;
      --green-light: #a8c9a0;
      --bg: #f8f6f1;
      --text: #2c2c2c;
      --white: #ffffff;
    }
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    body { font-family: 'Georgia', 'Noto Serif SC', serif; color: var(--text); background: var(--bg); }
    a { text-decoration: none; color: inherit; }

    nav {
      display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
      padding: 1.5rem 3rem; background: var(--white);
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.06); position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 100;
    }
    .logo { font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: bold; color: var(--green-dark); }
    .logo span { color: var(--green); }
    nav ul { display: flex; gap: 2rem; list-style: none; }
    nav ul li a { font-size: 0.95rem; transition: color 0.2s; }
    nav ul li a:hover { color: var(--green); }
    .nav-right { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1rem; }
    .cart-icon { font-size: 1.2rem; cursor: pointer; position: relative; }
    .back-btn {
      padding: 0.4rem 1rem; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 20px;
      background: var(--white); cursor: pointer; font-size: 0.85rem;
    }
    .back-btn:hover { border-color: var(--green); color: var(--green); }

    .about-hero {
      text-align: center; padding: 4rem 2rem;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--green-light), var(--bg));
    }
    .about-hero h1 { font-size: 2.5rem; color: var(--green-dark); margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .about-hero p { font-size: 1.1rem; color: #555; max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; }

    .about-section {
      max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 3rem 2rem;
    }
    .about-section h2 { font-size: 1.8rem; color: var(--green-dark); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
    .about-section p { font-size: 1rem; color: #555; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .values { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr)); gap: 2rem; margin-top: 2rem; }
    .value-card { background: var(--white); padding: 2rem; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); text-align: center; }
    .value-card h3 { font-size: 1.2rem; color: var(--green-dark); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
    .value-card p { font-size: 0.9rem; color: #666; }

    .contact-section {
      max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 3rem 2rem 4rem; text-align: center;
    }
    .contact-section h2 { font-size: 1.8rem; color: var(--green-dark); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
    .contact-card {
      background: var(--white); padding: 2.5rem; border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); margin-top: 1.5rem;
    }
    .contact-item { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
    .contact-item label { display: block; font-size: 0.85rem; color: #999; margin-bottom: 0.3rem; }
    .contact-item a { font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--green-dark); font-weight: bold; }
    .contact-item a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

    footer { text-align: center; padding: 2rem; background: var(--green-dark); color: var(--white); }
    footer p { font-size: 0.9rem; opacity: 0.8; }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      nav { padding: 1rem 1.5rem; }
      nav ul { display: none; }
      .about-hero h1 { font-size: 2rem; }
      .about-section, .contact-section { padding: 2rem 1rem; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <nav>
    <div class="logo">Pyq <span>Tea</span></div>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="/">首页</a></li>
      <li><a href="/about">关于我们</a></li>
    </ul>
    <div class="nav-right">
      <a href="/" class="back-btn">← 返回首页</a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <section class="about-hero">
    <h1>关于 Pyq Tea</h1>
    <p>致力于将中国精品茶叶带给世界各地的茶友，每一片茶叶都经过精心挑选，确保品质与正宗。</p>
  </section>

  <section class="about-section">
    <h2>我们的故事</h2>
    <p>Pyq Tea 创立于 2026 年，源于对中国茶文化的热爱与分享的愿望。我们与各大茶产区建立了直接合作关系，从龙井到普洱，从铁观音到茉莉花茶，每一款茶叶都来自原产地，由经验丰富的茶农手工采摘制作。</p>
    <p>我们相信，好茶不应该只留在产地。通过 Cloudflare 全球网络，我们将中国精品茶叶带给欧美及全球茶友，让更多人体验东方茶文化的魅力。</p>

    <h2 style="margin-top: 3rem;">我们的价值观</h2>
    <div class="values">
      <div class="value-card">
        <h3>🌿 原产地直供</h3>
        <p>所有茶叶直接来自产区，无中间商，确保新鲜与正宗。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-card">
        <h3>✋ 手工采摘</h3>
        <p>传统工艺，手工制作，保留茶叶最本真的风味。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-card">
        <h3>🌍 全球配送</h3>
        <p>通过全球物流网络，将茶叶送达世界各地。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-card">
        <h3>✅ 品质保证</h3>
        <p>每批茶叶经过严格品控，确保符合出口标准。</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="contact-section" id="contact">
    <h2>联系我们</h2>
    <p>如有任何问题或合作意向，欢迎通过以下方式联系我们：</p>
    <div class="contact-card">
      <div class="contact-item">
        <label>邮箱</label>
        <a href={`mailto:${contactEmail}`}>{contactEmail}</a>
      </div>
      <div class="contact-item">
        <label>网站</label>
        <a href="https://tea.pyqhintl.com">tea.pyqhintl.com</a>
      </div>
      <div class="contact-item">
        <label>营业时间</label>
        <p>周一至周五 9:00 - 18:00（北京时间）</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer>
    <p>© 2026 Pyq Tea — 精品中国茶 · tea.pyqhintl.com</p>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
